data.description: This 1408 square foot single family home has 3 bedrooms and 2.0 bathrooms. This home is located at 106 Lloyd St, Cary, IL 60013.
data.whatILove: Lovely CAPE COD home with 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms.  Large EAT-IN kitchen with WHITE CABINETS and a separate DINING ROOM with a nice bay window. The bedroom on the 1st floor can also be used as an office.  SPACIOUS master bedroom is upstairs along with another nicely sized bedroom. FINISHED BASEMENT with GREAT ROOM and a large room for STORAGE.  FENCED yard offers plenty of space.  This is such a nice, bright and airy home in a great community that is close to shopping, schools and Metra.  Come and take a look!
